java.lang.Object

edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configurationSpecification.XilinxV5DeviceClassGenerator
public class XilinxV5DeviceClassGenerator extends XilinxDeviceClassGenerator
This class generates Java source files that describe Xilinx device specifications for the virtex5 architecture.

      public XilinxV5DeviceClassGenerator()
